Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.49,0:00:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.23,0:00:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 2次元君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.51,0:00:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說你很無聊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.11,0:00:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.23,0:00:12.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
